data.description: This home is the absolute definition of ''turn-key''. From solar panels and a brand-new roof to new carpet, paint and appliances the list of improvements are too long to list in this description (ask for the list)! With over 90k worth of improvements this home sits ready to go on a corner lot and with NO HOA. With one of the larger lots in the Montara community, you will find yourself walking distance to a fantastic neighborhood green belt and community parks. Welcome home!
